    <summary><span data-ttu-id="52f78-101">指定是否应验证 <see cref="T:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SamlSecurityToken" /> 安全令牌的 <see cref="T:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SamlAudienceRestrictionCondition" />。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="52f78-101">Specifies whether the <see cref="T:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SamlSecurityToken" /> security token's <see cref="T:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SamlAudienceRestrictionCondition" /> should be validated.</span></span></summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="52f78-102">在采用颁发 <xref:System.IdentityModel.Selectors.AudienceUriMode> 安全令牌的安全令牌服务 (STS) 的联合应用程序中，应使用 <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SamlSecurityToken> 属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="52f78-102">Use the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Selectors.AudienceUriMode> property in a federated application that utilizes a security token service (STS) that issues <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SamlSecurityToken> security tokens.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="52f78-103">当 STS 颁发安全令牌时，它可以通过将 <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SamlAudienceRestrictionCondition> 添加到安全令牌中，来指定安全令牌的目标 Web 服务的 URI。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="52f78-103">When the STS issues the security token, it can specify the URI of the Web services for which the security token is intended by adding a <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SamlAudienceRestrictionCondition> to the security token.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="52f78-104">这样，通过指定应采用以下方式执行此检查，接收方 Web 服务的 <xref:System.IdentityModel.Selectors.SamlSecurityTokenAuthenticator> 将能够验证颁发的安全令牌是否针对此 Web 服务：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="52f78-104">That allows the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Selectors.SamlSecurityTokenAuthenticator> for the recipient Web service to verify that the issued security token is intended for this Web service by specifying that this check should happen by doing the following:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="52f78-105">将 <xref:System.IdentityModel.Selectors.SamlSecurityTokenAuthenticator.AudienceUriMode%2A> 属性设置为 Always 或 BearerKeyOnly。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="52f78-105">Set the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Selectors.SamlSecurityTokenAuthenticator.AudienceUriMode%2A> property to Always or BearerKeyOnly.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="52f78-106">通过将 URI 添加到 <xref:System.IdentityModel.Selectors.SamlSecurityTokenAuthenticator.AllowedAudienceUris%2A> 集合，从而指定有效的 URI 集。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="52f78-106">Specify the set of valid URIs, by adding the URIs to the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Selectors.SamlSecurityTokenAuthenticator.AllowedAudienceUris%2A> collection.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="52f78-107">（可选）重写 <xref:System.IdentityModel.Selectors.SamlSecurityTokenAuthenticator.ValidateAudienceRestriction%2A> 方法以指定要用于允许的 URI 的验证算法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="52f78-107">Optionally, override the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Selectors.SamlSecurityTokenAuthenticator.ValidateAudienceRestriction%2A> method to specify the validation algorithm to use for the allowed URI.</span></span>  
  
 ]]></format>
